    "page": 30,
    "text": "30\nCHAPTER 03\nGETTING\nSTARTED\n“You got the basics? Good, I hate\nrepeatin’ myself. Next bit’s the easy bit,\ngettin’ some warm bodies at yer back.\nEvery raider knows the best way to win\na fight is to ‘ave more bruisers than the\nother guy, or failin’ that, better guns than ‘em. But just as\nimportant as how many bullets yer slingin’, is who you’ve\ngot firin’ ‘em. Who that’ll be depends on yer style. if you\nwanna smack ‘em about, give ‘em a good shankin’ or just\npop their heads from a bit away, who you hire depends on\nyour preferred flavor o’ violence.\"\n30\nFALLOUT: FACTIONS – BATTLE FOR NUKA-WORLD | 03: Getting Started"
