nd writes a “1” in the Control box for that Location,\nas well as their Control Total box. Then they write the\nLocation’s name in their Home Turf box.\nThe Quest Begins …\nThe player turns to their Faction List, and chooses one of the\nQuest Lines available to them. They copy the Tier 1 Quest to\ntheir Story Sheet, as described on pg. 37-39.\nEasy First Ride\nThe player’s crew skips the Treat the Wounded step of the\nStory Phase after this game."
