    "text": "53\nFALLOUT: FACTIONS – BATTLE FOR NUKA-WORLD | APPENDIX 1: Scenarios\nSCENARIO DETAILS\nThe game lasts for five Rounds, or until a crew Retreats.\nSCENARIO POINTS\nAt the end of the game, if there are more Defending models left\non the Battlefield than Attacking models, the Defender wins.\nOtherwise, the Attacker wins.\nSTORY OUTCOMES\nThe Attacker gains an Experience Point if the Defender’s Leader\nwas Incapacitated.\nThe Defender gains an Experience Point if they survive to the\nend of the fourth Round without Retreating.\nThe winning crew can make an extra Story Action in the Story\nPhase after this game.\nSPECIAL PLOY: CACHED SPOILS\nThe Defender can use this Ploy at the start of any Round\nafter the first to immediately place 2 Search Tokens on the\nBattlefield. Each one must be within 1\" of a Defending model.\nIn the Defender’s first Turn, their Active model can make a\nRummage Action for free, without taking Fatigue."
